messages.messageBody:
Hi Folks!
I was referred to your group by a friend here in Florida, and it's so nice to find your
group. We are an unschooling family with 4 sons, ages 12, 10, 8 and 6 and have been
unschooling for 8 years, we love it! We love the freedom!

We're located in Central Florida and hope to participate in your discussions.

Happy Holidays!
Mellanie
